<i>adverb</i>: 충실히 [충실히], 지성껏 [지성껃], 극진히 [극찐히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>충실히 [충실히]</dt><br>
<dd>faithfully; loyally; devotedly; truly</dd><br>
<dd>충성스럽고 정직하며 성실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a loyal, honest, and sincere manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>지성껏 [지성껃]</dt><br>
<dd>faithfully; devotedly</dd><br>
<dd>온갖 정성을 다하여.</dd><br>
<dd>With all one's heart.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>극진히 [극찐히]</dt><br>
<dd>devotedly</dd><br>
<dd>마음과 힘을 다하여 매우 정성스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>With great care and with all one's heart and strength.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>